{
  "texts": [
    "Here, named entities refer to real-world objects such as persons, organisations, locations, dates, and quantities 35.",
    "The task of NER involves analysing text and identifying spans of words that correspond to named entities.",
    "NER algorithms typically use machine learning such as recurrent neural networks or transformers to automatically learn patterns and features from labelled training data.",
    "NER models are trained on annotated datasets where human annotators label entities in text.",
    "These annotations serve as the ground truth for training the model."
  ]
}